queryResponse.sql:
-- use existing price_requests_last in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVNGR1678126200557_price_requests_last
SELECT
    price_requests.price_request_id  AS "price_requests.price_request_id",
    price_requests.shipper_application_id  AS "price_requests.shipper_application_id",
        (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(price_requests.created_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) AS "price_requests.created_date",
    price_request_automated_strike_price_responses."BID_TO_DAT"  AS "price_request_automated_strike_price_responses.bid_to_dat",
        (CASE WHEN price_request_automated_strike_price_responses."BID_MADE_AT_THIS_LEVEL"  THEN 'Yes' ELSE 'No' END) AS "praspr.bid_made_at_this_level",
    price_request_automated_strike_price_responses."MARGIN_DOLLARS"  AS "price_request_automated_strike_price_responses.margin_dollars",
    price_request_automated_strike_price_responses."EXPECTED_MARGIN_DOLLARS"  AS "praspr.expected_margin_dollars",
    price_request_automated_strike_price_responses."PWIN"  AS "price_request_automated_strike_price_responses.pwin",
    price_requests.dat_rate  AS "price_requests.dat_rate"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.custom_trunc_price_requests  AS price_requests
INNER JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVNGR1678126200557_price_requests_last AS price_requests_last ON price_requests_last.price_request_id = price_requests.price_request_id and
      price_requests_last.shipper_application_id = price_requests.shipper_application_id
LEFT JOIN mlp_prod.public.automated_strike_price_responses  AS price_request_automated_strike_price_responses ON (price_request_automated_strike_price_responses."PRICE_REQUEST_ID") = price_requests.id
WHERE (price_requests.price_request_id ) IN (80215373, 80293709) AND (NOT (price_requests.is_test_quote::boolean ) OR (price_requests.is_test_quote::boolean ) IS NULL) AND (iff((nullif(price_requests.external_id, '')) is null, true, coalesce(price_requests_last.is_last_priced,false)) ) AND (price_requests.source not in ('shipment_creation', 'auto_accept_reject') )
GROUP BY
    (TO_DATE(CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST(price_requests.created_at  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))),
    1,
    2,
    4,
    5,
    6,
    7,
    8,
    9
ORDER BY
    4
FETCH NEXT 500 ROWS ONLY
